.TH WLA\-HUC6280 1 "November 2023" "WLA-DX 10.6" "WLA DX Assembler"
.SH NAME
wla\-huc6280 \- WLA DX cross-assembler for the HuC6280 (PC Engine)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wla\-huc6280
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.B \-o
.I output.o
.I source.asm
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B wla\-huc6280
assembles HuC6280 source code to a WLA DX object file.
The HuC6280 is a 65C02-based CPU used in the NEC PC Engine (TurboGrafx-16).
.PP
All WLA DX assemblers share an identical command-line interface.
For full option descriptions, examples, and a list of all supported CPU
architectures, see
.BR wla\-6502 (1).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR wla\-6502 (1),
.BR wla\-65c02 (1),
.BR wlalink (1)
